title: Canberra and War: the Australian War Memorial
abstract: To commemorate the Centenary of Canberra, the Australian War Memorial offers this selection of titles.
description: A place for remembrance, celebration, ceremony and protest, the Australian War Memorial in Canberra has compiled this selection of titles as part of the Centenary of Canberra events held in 2013. The program also features other icons of Canberra: Duntroon Royal Military College and old Parliament House and some famous faces, with Vivien Leigh, Laurence Olivier and HRH Queen Elizabeth.
